data.text:
I am very interested in hearing from you about the issues that are important to you.

Due to the large volume of letters, emails and faxes I receive, I am only able to accept messages from residents of the 28th Congressional District of Texas. Congressional courtesy dictates that Representatives be given the opportunity to assist their own constituents.

Please provide the following information to help determine whether you reside within the 28th District of Texas:
